description: Ensures every id attribute value is unique
failureSummary: Fix any of the following::  Document has multiple static elements with the same id attribute
help: id attribute value must be unique

description: Ensures the order of headings is semantically correct
failureSummary: Fix any of the following::  Heading order invalid
help: Heading levels should only increase by one

description: Landmarks must have a unique role or role/label/title (i.e. accessible name) combination
failureSummary: Fix any of the following::  The landmark must have a unique aria-label, aria-labelledby, or title to make landmarks distinguishable

description: Ensures <meta name=viewport"> can scale a significant amount"
failureSummary: Fix any of the following::  <meta> tag limits zooming on mobile devices
help: Users should be able to zoom and scale the text up to 500%

description: Ensure that the page, or at least one of its frames contains a level-one heading
failureSummary: Fix all of the following::  Page must have a level-one heading
help: Page must contain a level-one heading

description: Ensures tabindex attribute values are not greater than 0
failureSummary: Fix any of the following::  Element has a tabindex greater than 0
help: Elements should not have tabindex greater than zero
